{"text_id":120994,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," explore"," the"," properties"," of"," field"," dependent"," quasi","particles"," in"," the"," infinite"," dimensional"," Hubbard"," model","."," The"," Hubbard"," model"," is"," a"," well","-","established"," theoretical"," framework"," that"," describes"," the"," electronic"," behavior"," of"," strongly"," correlated"," materials","."," However",","," the"," Hubbard"," model"," in"," infinite"," dimensions"," is"," particularly"," interesting"," because"," it"," provides"," a"," simple"," yet"," accurate"," description"," of"," the"," electronic"," structure"," of"," many"," real"," materials","."," Our"," goal"," in"," this"," study"," is"," to"," investigate"," the"," behavior"," of"," quasi","particles"," in"," the"," Hubbard"," model"," when"," subjected"," to"," an"," external"," magnetic"," field","."," Specifically",","," we"," explore"," how"," the"," quasi","particles","'"," effective"," mass",","," quasi","particle"," weight",","," and"," band"," structure"," change"," in"," response"," to"," the"," applied"," field","."," We"," employ"," various"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," techniques",","," including"," Green","'","s"," function"," theory"," and"," the"," density"," matrix"," renormal","ization"," group"," method",","," to"," provide"," a"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," these"," field","-","dependent"," quasi","particle"," properties",".","Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," quasi","particles"," in"," the"," infinite"," dimensional"," Hubbard"," model"," exhibit"," a"," rich"," and"," complex"," behavior"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," an"," external"," magnetic"," field","."," Interestingly",","," our"," findings"," suggest"," that"," the"," quasi","particle"," weight"," and"," effective"," mass"," can"," vary"," rapidly"," and"," discontin","uously"," upon"," increasing"," the"," magnetic"," field"," strength","."," Furthermore",","," we"," observe"," significant"," changes"," in"," the"," band"," structure"," of"," the"," Hubbard"," model"," under"," the"," influence"," of"," a"," magnetic"," field","."," Our"," study"," sheds"," new"," light"," on"," the"," behavior"," and"," properties"," of"," quasi","particles"," in"," the"," Hubbard"," model",","," and"," provides"," important"," insights"," for"," understanding"," the"," electronic"," structure"," of"," strongly"," correlated"," materials"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," external"," fields","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}